                <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-3" style="color: #a6b443;">Child #2: Down Syndrome Special Needs</h4>
                <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">
                  "My second child has Down Syndrome and had sleep, snoring, breathing, and speech issues.
                  Though there were initial challenges, Dr. Ombrello created a customized plan unique to
                  this child's needs."
                </p>
                <div class="bg-green-50 p-4 rounded-lg">
                  <p class="text-green-700 text-sm">
                    <strong>Amazing Results:</strong> Major improvements in speech, sleep quality,
                    and overall systemic health!
                  </p>
